{"tid":2136501,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"俄擬10月推行大型疫苗接種計劃","createTime":"2020-08-02T07:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T07:55:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6621a9604c4d820c005e049f80954b5fef3b7790","tid":2136501,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T07:54:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200802/3LMHTPB5S4O6Y7PALUQESXDST4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200802%2F3LMHTPB5S4O6Y7PALUQESXDST4%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnftobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=fc0a26a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200802%2F3LMHTPB5S4O6Y7PALUQESXDST4%2F&h=fa6e6405\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200802/3LMHTPB5S4O6Y7PALUQESXDST4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n俄擬10月推行大型疫苗接種計劃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/s-X0bwtQK6WF5X0DrvET3jtNVwg=/640x437/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EA3QITUBJRCLBPKEQ7IRKVXXIA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fs-X0bwtQK6WF5X0DrvET3jtNVwg%3D%2F640x437%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEA3QITUBJRCLBPKEQ7IRKVXXIA.jpg&h=8ac27ab3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n福西（右）前日作證時與議員「鬆踭」打招呼。路透社<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯聲稱武漢肺炎疫苗已完成臨床實驗，準備於10月推行大型疫苗接種計劃，醫生和教師將率先接種，若成事將成全球首例。惟美國傳染病專家福西質疑俄羅斯和中國研發的疫苗是否安全。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：夏令營260人確診 美證兒童易播毒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n福西質疑中俄疫苗安全性<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯衞生部長穆拉什科向當地傳媒透露，國營的加馬列亞研究所（Gamaleya Institute）已完成臨床實驗，正準備文件為疫苗正式註冊，「計劃在10月推行大型接種」。消息指，疫苗會於本月內獲政府批核，及後將分發給醫護人員接種。惟當局未有公佈任何科學數據證明疫苗的安全和成效。俄羅斯昨日新增5,462宗確診個案，再有95人染疫死亡，累計逾84.5萬人確診，逾1.4萬人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯直接投資基金。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n全球有至少四款疫苗已進入第三階段的人體實驗，。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/法新社/美聯社"},{"pid":"a458fb9edc70645b3a28618df1fd2b2975647366","tid":2136501,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T07:55:48.000Z","msg":"西九龍影相手足被控襲警 聽朝9:30西九龍裁判法院提堂<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2136461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2136461</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q4t2qNS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ4t2qNS.jpg&h=ab4293ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n🟥旁聽好浪費時間喎～<br />\n🔴被告花既時間多啲定你？"}]}